"instead of `ssh`). Which means you don't need to install anything special in"
" a VM you want to manage. Additionally, for each target VM, `salt-ssh` is "
"started from a temporary VM. This way dom0 doesn't directly interact with "
"potentially malicious target VMs; and in the case of a compromised Salt VM, "
"because they are temporary, the compromise cannot spread from one VM to "
"another."
